description.narrative: UNICEF continued its support to strengthen the electronic Health Management Information System, the so-called Birth Registry (BR). During 2019 UNICEF supported the Ministry for IDPs from the Occupied Territories, Labor, Health and Social Affairs (MoIDPOTLHSA) in introducing practical steps towards utilizing the BR for performance monitoring of antenatal clinics and maternities starting from 2020. Besides, the quality of registered data has been audited to validate the information derived from the system. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:11/12/2019
